title: Bobby Decides On Songs He'll Perform With Brooks and Dunn + Morgan2 Asked Out On A Coffee Date + Leigh Nash From Sixpence None The Richer On Meeting David Letterman
itunes:title: Bobby Decides On Songs He'll Perform With Brooks and Dunn + Morgan2 Asked Out On A Coffee Date + Leigh Nash From Sixpence None The Richer On Meeting David Letterman
description:
Bobby was given the option to pick three Brooks and Dunn songs for them to perform at the Raging Idiots' Million Dollar Show. He made his pick for the final song today! 'PHD Peter' slid into our mailbag to ask Morgan2 out on a coffee date this weekend. Leigh Nash from Sixpence None The Richer stops by and talks to us about meeting David Letterman.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
